answers.body_markdown:
In my case I had this dependency, pointing to an specific version:

        &lt;dependency&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;org.junit.platform&lt;/groupId&gt;
            &lt;artifactId&gt;junit-platform-commons&lt;/artifactId&gt;
            &lt;version&gt;{version}&lt;/version&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;

It worked after removing the version:

        &lt;dependency&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;org.junit.platform&lt;/groupId&gt;
            &lt;artifactId&gt;junit-platform-commons&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;/dependency&gt;

